title: Whistle! W
alternative_title: ホイッスル！W ; Whistle! Double W
status: ホイッスル！W ; Whistle! Double W
description:
Description :
        Tenjou Kouga is a 6th grader at Musashinomori elementary with a good sense for soccer. However everything around him is starting to change when a soccer genius named Kurose Takumi transfers to his school and sparks a new passion for soccer inside Kouga!
